default3.4
default defaultWomen and girls with disabilities are twice as likely to experience gender based violence 
defaultas
default non-disabled peers
default.  In settings where arms are readily available, 
defaultrisks to women and children increasedefault  with weapons used to 
defaultboth threaten and implement violence
