default 
defaultcompletion. DFID’s support to mine action will fall short of 
defaultachieving 
defaultits 
defaultVfM
default potential if clearance and mine risk education does not connect to victim assistance efforts.
default
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultRatify the UK Arms Trade Treaty
default.  
default Support States
default to consider the risk of arms diversion and assess 
defaulthow
default export of conventional arms, ammunition, or components 
defaultcould 
defaultundermine peace and security or be used in facilitating serious violations of international human rights.  
default 
default
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultR
defaulteduce and prevent the risks, impact, and incidence of armed violence by 
defaultpromoting comprehensive responses to the issues of Community Safety and Security and Small Arms and Light Weapons Control and 
defaultimproving services that provide immediate and longer-term health, psychological
